{"id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "Bepje van den Burg, Head of Medical Business Clients and Professionals at ABN AMRO, discusses with an expert panel, consisting of [Richard Verbrugge](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/expert-academy/security-awareness-onderwijs.html) (Information Security Risk Manager at ABN AMRO), Erwin Hotting (Cybersecurity Executive Advisor at Threadstone) and Jeroen Daems (dentist owner at De Tandentent), concrete solutions to strengthen digital security, without unnecessarily burdening daily practice.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap", "source_title": "Cybersecurity in the digital healthcare landscape", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap.html", "source_date": "2025-10-15", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "- Make sure you have your basic protection in order.\n- Security is more than IT.\n- Know what you need to protect and take measures.\n- Teach your employees to recognize and report phishing emails.\n- Start implementing NIS2 on time and bring your suppliers with you.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap", "source_title": "Cybersecurity in the digital healthcare landscape", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap.html", "source_date": "2025-10-15", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap", "source_title": "Cybersecurity in the digital healthcare landscape", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap.html", "source_date": "2025-10-15", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap", "source_title": "Cybersecurity in the digital healthcare landscape", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/cyberveiligheid-in-het-digitale-zorglandschap.html", "source_date": "2025-10-15", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 12, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
